Definition: a written instrument legally conveying property to a trustee often used to secure an obligation such as a mortgage or promissory note
Synonyms: deed_of_trust, legal_document, noun, group, law, c, a, written, instrument, legally, conveying, property, to, trustee, often, used, secure, an, obligation, such, as, mortgage, or, promissory, note
Category: noun.communication
